Package de.codesourcery.eve.apiclient.exceptions

Exception Summary
APIErrorException Thrown when a response from the Eve Online(tm) API indicated an error.
AuthenticationFailureException Thrown when authentication with the EVE Online(tm) API failed.
CredentialsInvalidatedException Thrown when trying to use an invalidated credentials object.
InvalidCredentialsException Thrown when the server rejected the supplied credentials (login failed).
MissingAPIKeyException Thrown when an action required an API key of a specific type but no suitable key could be found.
UnknownCredentialsException Thrown when credentials for a given character ID could not be retrieved.
UserAccountStoreLockedException Thrown when trying to access a locked credentials store.
